Plan a {word_count}-word SEO blog post.

Topic: {topic}
Target keyword: {target_keyword}
Audience: {audience}
Tone: {tone}

Provide:
1. Central argument (one sentence — what does this post claim or prove?)
2. Intro hook angle (the specific question, stat, or scenario that opens the post)
3. 4 main sections: section title, one-sentence summary of its argument, one concrete example or data point to include
4. Conclusion angle (the key takeaway and what action the reader should take)
5. Keyword placement notes (where target keyword and variants should appear naturally)

Be specific. This plan will be followed by three separate writing agents.

